OL,3,CLondon Underground strikes risk safety
OL,4,Cof blind people, charity warns
OL,6,FThe charity supporting people with
OL,7,Fsight loss has issued a warning that
OL,8,Fnext week's strikes on London
OL,9,FUnderground risks significantly
OL,10,Fimpacting the independence and safety
OL,11,Fof blind and partially sighted people.
OL,13,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,14,FTransport union (RMT) are due to walk
OL,15,Fout for 24 hours from 12 noon on
OL,16,FTuesday April 21 and again at the same
OL,17,Ftime on Thursday April 23 in a dispute
OL,18,Fover shift patterns.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
