OL,3,CLondon Underground strikes risk safety
OL,4,Cof blind people, charity warns
OL,6,FTransport for London (TfL) has warned
OL,7,Fof disruption to Tube services if the
OL,8,Faction goes ahead.
OL,10,FGuide Dogs UK said for many blind and
OL,11,Fpartially sighted people, the London
OL,12,FUnderground is a vital and familiar
OL,13,Fnetwork and when it is disrupted,
OL,14,Falternative routes are often less
OL,15,Faccessible, predictable, or safe.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
