OL,3,CLondon Underground strikes risk safety
OL,4,Cof blind people, charity warns
OL,6,F"Tube closures can lead to increased
OL,7,Ftraffic, busier pavements, and more
OL,8,Fcrowded public spaces and buses. We
OL,9,Falso expect greater use of e-bikes and
OL,10,Fe-scooters, and as we saw last year,
OL,11,Fmany of these were poorly parked and
OL,12,Fblocked pavements, posing risks for
OL,13,Fpedestrians with sight loss.
OL,15,F"For some, these factors may make
OL,16,Fjourneys feel unpredictable or unsafe,
OL,17,Fand may lead them to avoid travelling
OL,18,Faltogether, limiting their
OL,19,Findependence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
